start_direct_message_with_user: Start direct message with user. Example: /startdm userId1
join_room_with_address: Join room with address. Example: /join address1 address2
invite_user_to_room: Invite user to room. Example: /invite userId1 userId2 [-r reason]
disinvite_user_to_room: Disinvite user to room. Example: /disinvite userId1 userId2 [-r reason]
kick_user_from_room: Kick user from room. Example: /kick userId1 userId2 servername [-r reason]
ban_user_from_room: Ban user from room. Example: /ban userId1 userId2 servername [-r reason]
unban_user_from_room: Unban user from room. Example: /unban userId1 userId2
change_profile_picture_in_current_room: Change profile picture in current room. Example /myroomavatar mxc://xyzabc
delete_messages_from_users: Delete messages from users. Example: /delete userId1 servername -past 1d|2h|5m|30s [-t m.room.message] [-r spam]
manage_server_access_control_list: Manage server access control list. Example /acl [-a servername1] [-d servername2] [-ra servername1] [-rd servername2]
